01:41.960 --> 01:45.220
I'm looking at the bottom of hubcaps, you know, trying to keep this thing going straight.

01:46.000 --> 01:50.920
And God I had a vision at that point of a world where trucks ran forever on and on and

01:50.920 --> 01:52.060
on, through and around the whole planet.

01:52.500 --> 01:53.580
I said, how can we do that?

01:54.000 --> 01:56.920
So I had to develop a whole plant and a culture to get them there.

01:57.260 --> 02:00.620
And by the time I'd done it and written the book, they had to say, I feel it's incomplete.

02:01.280 --> 02:02.780
How did they get there in the first place?

02:03.100 --> 02:04.540
