02:39.520 --> 02:44.560
of technology and a little bit of politics and the first one is some ways like a make-room,

02:44.680 --> 02:48.500
make-room and so where are we going to go if we don't get a hold of technology and what

02:48.500 --> 02:49.180
we can do.

02:49.660 --> 02:55.980
If you notice there's a very, the first book shows you how rotten Britain will be five

02:55.980 --> 02:59.920
hundred years from now, the third book, how rotten America will be five hundred years

02:59.920 --> 03:05.580
